{"tid":684364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二十度，日本人穿浴袍撥扇","createTime":"2018-05-30T12:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T13:16:07.000Z","uid":132027,"like":7,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ae06f5b4001c42ffe95fe7a9ddc76d5b16d60d0","tid":684364,"uid":132027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"二十度，日本人穿浴袍撥扇；火山專家在瘋狂焗桑拿。 <br />\n三十度，美國人開冷氣機；火山專家在太陽下打邊爐。 <br />\n四十度，英國人在車子熱死了；火山專家在車子後座做劇烈運動。 <br />\n五十度，泰國人在市內裸奔；火山專家試穿長袖毛衣。 <br />\n六十度，阿拉伯人瘋狂喝冰水；火山專家寫意地喝熱咖啡。 <br />\n八十度，非洲人躲在雪櫃裡；火山專家改穿短衫短褲，等待真正的夏天到來。 <br />\n一百度，水份完全蒸發，大量動物被活活熱死；火山專家覺得要稍為補充水份。 <br />\n一千度，熔岩淹沒都市，建築物被高溫融化；火山專家終於說：『老天，外面好熱！』 <br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始回暖了！』"},{"pid":"d6c5616a1aba309a0ad3c209c620287dfd8c6b4d","tid":684364,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cef79b7b18c02e91e75294e52705b51ba50228f","tid":684364,"uid":1991,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:08:16.000Z","msg":"好老實 一般"},{"pid":"1baa98ec5963b03f7f880701723b59dadab6079a","tid":684364,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:10:50.000Z","msg":"未睇哂都知講咩<br />\n<br />\n唔好笑"},{"pid":"8e42761148019f77203c94caa8e832d4887dd2da","tid":684364,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"🦐🦐🦐"},{"pid":"bfdf4cb633cf9d3d3b67273ae2e6604a17e6e050","tid":684364,"uid":59902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:12:39.000Z","msg":"小小尷 都ok 嘅"},{"pid":"b3ede06b54b2c11805e224a5794f4125242b5521","tid":684364,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"又話水份完全蒸發曬<br />\n仲點補充水份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b1314a21e043c066f6e3ee4757d7bd0a96b31